description:
Expand your track list with the Best of 90's Vol. 1 Song Pack! You need the full game Let's Sing Country to use this DLC. Includes hit songs:
• The Cure "Friday I'm In Love"
• Sinead O'Connor "Nothing Compares 2 U"
• All Saints "Never Ever"
• Aqua "Barbie Girl"
• Alanis Morissette "Ironic"
name: Let's Sing - Best of 90's Vol. 1 Song Pack
